<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for the New Year</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jan 03, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Lord,
</p>

 <p>
May I not confuse
</p>

 <p>
Naive, blind optimism <br></br>
with true hope,
</p>

 <p>
Self-righteous purity <br></br>
with true holiness,
</p>

 <p>
The voice of my own desires <br></br>
with the voice of the Lord,
</p>

 <p>
Or my own country <br></br>
with the Kingdom of God.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


